{"tid":1848302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[二百萬資深遊行黃絲同我入晒嚟] 作為香港人既你得返三條路揀","createTime":"2020-01-28T11:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T11:49:07.000Z","uid":88134,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d08ce426a178300c617c90795e0a6aeb43c7c479","tid":1848302,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T11:37:55.000Z","msg":"一係勇武<br />\n一係罷工/課<br />\n一係both<br />\n<br />\n唔好再做左膠拎光環啦，無人會多謝你，光環唔可以當飯食。<br />\n呢個wars肺炎又唔係有藥醫，你放佢入嚟其實同睇住佢死都無分別，但係就大大增加香港醫療系統既負擔、醫護專業人士感染同埋社區爆發既風險。<br />\n<br />\n唔好影張相出個story上instagram話自己撐醫護罷工就算撚數呀屌你地老味<br />\n學下輝明邨班藍絲啦，係你以為人地選書少既時候但係利益就係最大既知識，而民主去到最後都係講社會不同群體既利益，你地就當為咗自己條命為咗啲股樓，罷工啦。講到口臭，勇武唔求全民勇武，只求全民係體制外行多一步。而罷工就係和理非既大技。"},{"pid":"c3bf82a386fa1869b7ff28b6ef57ade8f6ca65dd","tid":1848302,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T11:39:15.000Z","msg":"罷工保平安"},{"pid":"1208ab36a10fd8fa16a0a2a45b1b12d0e6e7ff45","tid":1848302,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T11:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MpTV157.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMpTV157.png&h=a77d0703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽朝7:00 黎明行動 準時點人數</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠鐘推行動post啦"},{"pid":"17d99ee9beae4b1bf6ff4671e5c38b4ad81f57c6","tid":1848302,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T11:42:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F